            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">We accept all major credit cards through Stripe, cash on delivery, and GodPay. Payment is secure and processed safely.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-200">
